<i>♪ Did you want it bad? ♪</i>

00:32.741 --> 00:34.786
<i>♪ Oh, my ♪</i>

00:36.830 --> 00:38.915
<i>♪ It tears me apart ♪</i>

00:43.336 --> 00:45.463
<i>♪ We can try to hide it ♪</i>

00:47.674 --> 00:50.427
<i>♪ It's all the same ♪</i>

00:50.510 --> 00:53.054
<i>♪ I've been losing you ♪</i>

00:54.431 --> 00:56.599
