In my heart, in this cold heart ♪</i>

01:05.275 --> 01:09.279
<i>♪ I can live or I can die ♪</i>

01:09.738 --> 01:13.533
<i>♪ I believe if I just try ♪</i>

01:13.616 --> 01:19.873
<i>♪ You believe in you and I ♪</i>

01:21.332 --> 01:24.461
<i>♪ In you and I ♪</i>

01:25.837 --> 01:30.300
<i>♪ In you and I ♪</i>

01:30.383 --> 01:32.927
<i>♪ In you and I ♪</i>

02:02.582 --> 02:04.584
I pushed him.

02:04.667 --> 02:07.962
No, nobody pushed him.

02:10.215 --> 02:11.215
Nobody.

02:11.257 --> 02:14.260
<i>♪ Didn't I shake sugaree? ♪</i>

02:19.641 --> 02:22.477
<i>♪ Have a little song ♪</i>

02:22.560 --> 02:24.813
<i>♪ Won't take long ♪</i>

