That's kind of my MO right now.

19:15.864 --> 19:17.324
- Neutral.
- Yeah.

19:17.407 --> 19:20.202
Okay. I can do that.

19:29.920 --> 19:36.176
I am the greatest

19:37.219 --> 19:38.512
<i>monster.</i>

19:38.595 --> 19:45.310
<i>And I come to devour
two young chickadees!</i>

19:45.978 --> 19:47.813
My heavens.

19:49.606 --> 19:52.276
He was the best monster.

19:52.359 --> 19:55.821
- Show her the angry beaver.
