20:05.622 --> 20:08.166
Oh, here's the teacup one.

20:08.250 --> 20:09.877
How we doing here?

20:09.960 --> 20:11.712
We're showing Grandma
the memory book.

20:11.795 --> 20:13.088
It's wonderful.

20:14.840 --> 20:16.425
Here's <i>Guess How Much I Love You.</i>

20:16.508 --> 20:20.178
- That one's kind of boring.
