20:20.262 --> 20:22.097
We loved that book.

20:22.180 --> 20:23.724
Okay.

20:23.807 --> 20:26.935
<i>"He was almost too sleepy
to think anymore.</i>

20:27.019 --> 20:31.732
<i>Then he looked beyond the thorn bushes,
